feedback_text: John demonstrated strong problem-solving skills during the project. He effectively communicated his ideas to the team and was always willing to help others. His technical implementation was clean and well-documented.

Sarah showed great leadership in coordinating team meetings. Her technical contributions were solid, though she could improve her documentation. She worked well with others and maintained good communication throughout.

Mike's technical skills are excellent, but he sometimes struggled to explain complex concepts to team members. He was punctual and reliable in completing his tasks, contributing positively to team dynamics.
